spec_patches.description: Wave 1 spec patch: Added CRITICAL GENERATION REQUIREMENTS sections to both config workbook and migration file specs. Explicit min row counts, mandatory GL account placeholders, mandatory benefits IT sheets, mandatory Data Quality Review sheet, mandatory Cover sheet, explicit wage type catalog minimums with example WT codes.
Wave 3 spec patch: Added explicit requirements for PA coverage in IT0001, IT0210 2-row minimum, IT0041 2-row minimum, Federal geocode 00-000-0000 mandatory, GL account reinforcement.
Wave 4 patch: Added explicit ALL-TABS-REQUIRED table to config spec, ALL-CORE-INFOTYPES-REQUIRED list to migration spec. Approach controls DEPTH not PRESENCE.

Wave 5 mega patch: Added 18-item config workbook self-check checklist + 22-item migration file self-check checklist. Complete BSI geocode reference table (24 states). Tax rate columns mandatory. Union config enforcement. ZERO blank HKONT enforcement. Geocode format enforcement (XX-XXX-XXXX only). Conditional sheet triggers explicit. Pre-save validation gates.
